﻿WEBVTT

00:00:09.760 --> 00:00:17.960
Of a certain other individual or the
individual who has been caught, what to do?

00:00:17.985 --> 00:00:22.360
So, he is advised in the matter like this,

00:00:22.387 --> 00:00:28.102
first you put your own attention in your own
Sahasrara, this is the first thing you have to do.

00:00:28.152 --> 00:00:38.360
Then while chanting the mantra, put the attention on the
chakra of the person to whom you are giving treatment.

00:00:38.422 --> 00:00:43.320
And also, your attention should be
simultaneously on your own chakra.

00:00:43.344 --> 00:00:54.002
Then while chanting the mantra, you can give a flow of vibration or you can go on giving bandhana to that chakra.

00:00:55.432 --> 00:01:01.112
Now by chanting mantra only for a
time, may not release the chakra.

00:01:01.112 --> 00:01:05.222
So you have to repeat the chantings.

00:01:05.245 --> 00:01:15.016
Say, as you go on increasing the chanting, say 7 times, 10 times, 21 times, like that,

00:01:15.061 --> 00:01:20.691
and you find simultaneously when your attention is
there, you find that the chakra is getting relieved,

00:01:20.691 --> 00:01:27.958
it is getting opened and the Kundalini is
making its movement in a proper manner.

00:01:28.018 --> 00:01:35.728
So, that’s how you have to relieve a chakra while
chanting the mantra, with the help of mantra.

00:01:35.757 --> 00:01:38.257
That's we just told.

00:01:38.277 --> 00:01:44.687
Now, there was another question from Mr. Pitkar.

00:01:50.906 --> 00:02:00.499
He asked that a number of Sahaja Yogis who
find themselves stuck at certain chakra

00:02:00.499 --> 00:02:07.346
and they feel they don’t know how
to go ahead, what they should do?

00:02:07.346 --> 00:02:16.189
He says, we want to have certain tips
by which we can make quicker progress

00:02:16.249 --> 00:02:18.749
without getting
constricted at that point.

00:02:21.829 --> 00:02:28.536
Mataji expressed her desire that she wants to
participate in our brain trust programme today.

00:02:28.586 --> 00:02:31.753
And She has specifically asked me
to convey this message to you,

00:02:31.771 --> 00:02:38.163
that you should ask me questions for which you
want any... you have got any particular problem.

00:02:39.023 --> 00:02:47.366
She has expressed her happiness and pleasure at the way we are conducting, I have told her that we are conducting the brain trust programme as was desired by You.

00:02:47.366 --> 00:02:53.684
And She expressed her joy that "all right,
continue you have got my full blessings."

00:02:53.684 --> 00:03:01.866
I will request everybody that as soon as She comes only the
garlanding on behalf of the Shibir has been already done.

00:03:01.882 --> 00:03:08.044
Let Her be seated and we will continue the
programme as we have continued up till now.

00:03:08.094 --> 00:03:15.084
Only when in difficulty Mataji will participate
when and whenever She wants it being picked.

00:03:15.084 --> 00:03:26.696
[Same explained in Marathi.]

00:04:07.593 --> 00:04:44.180
[Shri Mataji is welcomed.]

00:04:47.139 --> 00:04:55.639
So, I was just now  translated the question
that was put forward by Mr. Pitkar.

00:04:57.289 --> 00:05:03.805
I will again repeat it. He wanted to know, he expressed that there are a number of Sahaja Yogis

00:05:03.808 --> 00:05:13.544
who find it difficult to take their Kundalini
above certain chakras, say Vishuddhi or Agnya.

00:05:13.544 --> 00:05:27.998
Frequently they get caught at these chakras and he wants to have certain tips on how to progress in Sahaja Yoga.

00:05:27.998 --> 00:05:31.514
How to bring Kundalini or stabilise
the Kundalini in Sahasrara.

00:05:34.618 --> 00:05:46.009
So, I think for me, I have talked to you on a
few occasions about my own experience about this

00:05:48.069 --> 00:06:01.849
and I have told you that, it is very much
necessary first to put your attention to yourself.

00:06:02.059 --> 00:06:08.731
This is the first thing you have to do. If you want to
make progress, you have to give attention to yourself.

00:06:08.765 --> 00:06:15.331
Don’t think about anybody, think
only about Mother and yourself.

00:06:15.367 --> 00:06:19.692
That’s all.

00:06:19.725 --> 00:06:24.235
If you put your attention to say your
brother, your friend, your sister,

00:06:24.235 --> 00:06:28.955
but you are actually doing is, you are sitting before
the photograph of Mother that is actually Mother.

00:06:28.964 --> 00:06:35.675
You are saying that, “Mother, I am walking towards
you and at the same time you are telling your mother

00:06:35.675 --> 00:06:39.197
that see my sister, she is not
feeling well you look after her”.

00:06:39.237 --> 00:06:43.547
So you are saying, chanting
one thing with your mouth

00:06:43.602 --> 00:06:48.762
and your attention is towards your sister and
not towards yourself and towards your Mother.

00:06:48.812 --> 00:06:51.152
So, your progress is arrested.

00:06:51.152 --> 00:06:59.322
That’s the principle reason why people
get obstructed. This is one thing.

00:06:59.372 --> 00:07:19.238
One more point I told you and that is regarding the habit of
forgiving all those who have offended you, knowingly or unknowingly

00:07:19.278 --> 00:07:28.448
and also apologising for any offending
that you might have done to others.

00:07:28.448 --> 00:07:31.352
And that you have to do from the heart of your heart.

00:07:31.388 --> 00:07:40.478
So, when you sit for meditation, you have to
first forgive others and then ask for apologies.

00:07:40.508 --> 00:07:46.328
But after forgiving you ask a question, put a
question to yourself, have you really forgiven?

00:07:46.383 --> 00:07:50.058
And within seconds you will come to
know that you have not really forgiven.

00:07:50.100 --> 00:07:55.461
It’s very difficult, it is a subtle thing
that you have to practice within yourself.

00:07:55.501 --> 00:07:59.691
And after doing this, what you are doing
actually you are trying to help yourself,

00:07:59.691 --> 00:08:08.051
your mind, your attention, your awareness
is all settled in a proper order.

00:08:08.051 --> 00:08:13.261
And then there is absolutely no difficulty,
Kundalini straight comes in Sahasrara

00:08:13.261 --> 00:08:23.655
and it descends down and there is continuous cool flow
of vibrations from all over body, while on your hands?

00:08:23.695 --> 00:08:30.125
So that is how it is to be done. And I don’t
think there is any other short cut for this,

00:08:30.165 --> 00:08:35.335
that is to be practiced within,
not from outside. Thank you!

00:08:37.985 --> 00:08:53.124
[Same explained in Marathi.]

00:12:13.889 --> 00:12:17.669
Can I ask a question to Mr. Chavan now?

00:12:22.366 --> 00:12:27.029
Shri Mataji asks in Marathi.

00:12:36.794 --> 00:12:42.689
The question is like this, I am asking Mr.
Chavan, he said you must forgive everyone.

00:12:42.689 --> 00:12:50.479
Now supposing somebody abuses your Mataji, says horrible
things about Her and see sort of infuriates you,

00:12:50.479 --> 00:12:54.169
then what to do? How to overcome that?

00:13:12.045 --> 00:13:17.676
[Mr Chavan replies in Marathi]

00:14:48.718 --> 00:14:59.054
Now, I’ll just try to again translate
in the reply that I gave was that,

00:14:59.964 --> 00:15:12.942
I feel that suppose a situation comes across
where a certain person is abusing Mother.

00:15:12.989 --> 00:15:15.489
So, what is our first reaction?

00:15:15.489 --> 00:15:29.429
If you are stable, I feel you should be immediately able to make out, as to whether that person is a knowledgeable person, whether he is realised,

00:15:29.459 --> 00:15:35.802
because a realised soul will never be able to abuse
Mother, never be able to talk anything against Mother.

00:15:35.822 --> 00:15:48.016
That is just impossible, it’s only because he is in avidya,
he doesn’t have the knowledge that he is abusing the Mother.

00:15:48.026 --> 00:15:52.856
When he comes to reality, he will not do so.

00:15:52.896 --> 00:16:04.696
Now, I told that our elder brother Shri Jesus
Christ, has shown us the way in this regard.

00:16:04.726 --> 00:16:09.246
He has said that whenever you come
across any such person who abuses God,

00:16:09.293 --> 00:16:19.987
then you have to tell, you have to pray God that please,
please we have to say please Mother, You forgive.

00:16:20.037 --> 00:16:23.938
And Mother forgives everything comes in it.

00:16:23.972 --> 00:16:27.837
I feel it is not necessary to give him
punishment. I am nobody to punish him.

00:16:28.208 --> 00:16:34.468
It is the forgiveness of the Mother itself will
act as punishment and reward for that person.

00:16:34.463 --> 00:16:39.308
Because as soon as She forgives, the person
will get realised and he will get everything.

00:16:39.328 --> 00:16:43.488
There is no other good punishment. Thank you!

00:16:51.113 --> 00:16:53.455
It’s very well said.

00:16:53.455 --> 00:16:59.925
But it’s a very subtle point you see because God has
given us also temper and anger as well as forgiveness.

00:16:59.955 --> 00:17:02.135
Both qualities are within us.

00:17:02.176 --> 00:17:09.452
And he has not given us temper for something
that is useless, as even temper is necessary.

00:17:09.496 --> 00:17:16.772
Once you are realised, once you are a realised
soul, your temper is also dynamic, it is needed.

00:17:16.772 --> 00:17:21.766
When somebody says something
against God and against your Mother,

00:17:21.815 --> 00:17:27.676
if he is a realized soul or if he is not a
realised soul is a very important point, no doubt.

00:17:27.716 --> 00:17:32.084
Supposing he is not a realised soul

00:17:32.116 --> 00:17:38.975
then the best thing is to pity such a man and say that “Oh
God forgive, because they do not know what they are doing”.

00:17:38.995 --> 00:17:48.327
But say even Christ, supposing something had happened
to the Mother of Christ, now how He would have reacted?

00:17:48.358 --> 00:17:57.617
Then he would have come up as her son and he would have
taken the cross in his hands and hit all the people there.

00:17:57.657 --> 00:18:02.717
So, when somebody abuses
who is a realised soul,

00:18:02.733 --> 00:18:09.917
there are many realised souls, whom I have
given realisation, who have come up very well,

00:18:09.945 --> 00:18:16.246
but who fall out, who try to
abuse and try to say bad things.

00:18:16.295 --> 00:18:20.016
Now at that time, it’s the whole
collectivity is challenged,

00:18:20.050 --> 00:18:24.036
the whole collectivity, the whole collective being
is challenged when he says something like that.

00:18:24.036 --> 00:18:28.226
He is a part and parcel of your being.

00:18:28.266 --> 00:18:31.993
Think if in your finger you have some
pain, what do you do? You rub it off.

00:18:35.372 --> 00:18:47.553
When a person who is a realised soul, if he tries to be
funny or if he tries to abuse anything that is divine,

00:18:47.593 --> 00:18:51.499
you have to get into a temper, that’s a part,

00:18:51.499 --> 00:18:56.542
but this temper is to be diverted into Sahaja Yoga system,

00:18:56.580 --> 00:19:01.747
like you beat him with shoes.

00:19:01.791 --> 00:19:05.647
You write his names and burn it.

00:19:05.678 --> 00:19:11.487
You write his names on
the ground and stamp it,

00:19:11.517 --> 00:19:18.222
you take out your anger on them. Your anger is divine
anger, it has a meaning. You are part of the whole Divine.

00:19:18.249 --> 00:19:26.572
If you are angry, the Divine is angry, but this anger is
‘hithkaari’, is the one that is benevolent, is a benevolent anger.

00:19:26.631 --> 00:19:36.021
This benevolent anger is necessary because he is
the part and parcel of the whole and you go all out.

00:19:36.057 --> 00:19:47.037
There are so many ways by which you really punish in a symbolic way. But that punishment brings him out of his negativity.

00:19:47.083 --> 00:19:53.222
But for people who are not realised
also, these things come up.

00:19:53.249 --> 00:19:59.272
When negativity is very powerful and wants
to take a challenge with the positivity.

00:19:59.293 --> 00:20:08.534
Supposing there’s a negative person
and he wants to disturb say our work,

00:20:08.570 --> 00:20:13.204
at that time you will be amazed that those who will
be negative will start supporting the person.

00:20:13.257 --> 00:20:16.934
Immediately, you can pick them out
and say that these are negative.

00:20:16.970 --> 00:20:20.574
And those who are positive will be in anger.

00:20:20.619 --> 00:20:26.414
They’ll keep quiet, some of them will be boiling and some
of them might get up and say, “You get out from here”.

00:20:29.011 --> 00:20:35.331
That we have to do, that challenge
we have to take up and say to people.

00:20:35.338 --> 00:20:41.414
That is only possible when you have
full discretion how to use your anger.

00:20:41.465 --> 00:20:50.791
You have to say it out. It is necessary because
if you allow these negativities to be there,

00:20:50.791 --> 00:20:56.864
they will get hold of people who are
sitting on the fences who are half-baked.

00:20:56.904 --> 00:21:04.834
At that time it is necessary to show your strength, not
to get lost in your temper. But to stand up to say,

00:21:04.893 --> 00:21:08.304
“You get out from here, don’t know what you are doing”.

00:21:08.336 --> 00:21:16.775
That is very important, because whatever,
you see, say, is a mantra, is a dynamite

00:21:16.802 --> 00:21:24.025
that will change the whole atmosphere. The negativity will
run away, but if you say that, “All right, let it happen”.

00:21:24.025 --> 00:21:26.525
It will have a bad effect.

00:21:28.381 --> 00:21:37.651
Christ allowed them to torture him, but not his Mother nor God.

00:21:37.685 --> 00:21:42.562
He took a hunter in his hand when
people were selling in the market.

00:21:42.602 --> 00:21:47.842
So, he has a double side also.
And in you also there is Kalki.

00:21:47.904 --> 00:21:50.801
And you, I have awakened Kalki in you.

00:21:50.854 --> 00:21:56.961
So, you are also Kalki. But you must reach
a certain maturity, then only you can do it.

00:21:56.961 --> 00:22:03.181
Sometimes it is very important, but the way you do
it, with what dignity you do it is very important.

00:22:03.181 --> 00:22:11.199
But one has to learn that also: you have to learn how to say
it with sternness and with strength that you shut up now.

00:22:11.230 --> 00:22:17.410
You are not to say a word, and only saying
this will make all the negativities run away.

00:22:17.490 --> 00:22:24.770
At a point, one has to say, that’s what I feel
that when you grow in this atmosphere here,

00:22:24.810 --> 00:22:33.701
let you find yourself which is also
very, very strong as well as forgiving.

00:22:33.701 --> 00:22:38.960
You know that your Mother’s nature is Atisoumya, Atiroudrya; She lives in two extremes.

00:22:38.979 --> 00:22:47.496
She can be extremely gentle, and she can be terrific.
And these two qualities you should also imbibe,

00:22:47.496 --> 00:22:52.719
but it should never be directed against your own brothers
and sisters, you don’t direct all destructive forces.

00:22:52.719 --> 00:22:57.694
But against the negativity, because
the time has come for us to fight.

00:22:57.742 --> 00:23:01.884
The time has started now for us to fight these negative forces

00:23:01.965 --> 00:23:09.682
and for that we all must take up strength within us, you see
compromising with them and all that is not going to help us.

00:23:09.682 --> 00:23:15.489
So, the strength must be there, a dignity and with
all understanding and discretion you have to tell.

00:23:15.489 --> 00:23:21.459
But I have seen mostly negative people will
stand up and say, “You shut up, you go away”.

00:23:21.479 --> 00:23:26.536
So, the positivity should reach that stage where you are
matured and when you just say “stand up and shut up”,

00:23:26.578 --> 00:23:30.036
it means something.

00:23:30.076 --> 00:23:42.094
That’s a part one has to play. One has to accept we are not going to run away from our parts and some time, as I said, you have to take swords in your hand.

00:23:42.117 --> 00:23:50.384
So, this is a very courageous role full of valour.

00:23:50.414 --> 00:23:54.674
It does not mean that we are
cowards, or we are weak people.

00:23:54.695 --> 00:23:59.934
We are very strong, extremely powerful
people and you have tremendous power.

00:23:59.953 --> 00:24:04.454
But you have the greatest
power is that of forgiveness,

00:24:04.533 --> 00:24:07.603
but behind that forgiveness, there is no weakness.

00:24:07.643 --> 00:24:17.353
What is the forgiveness of a weak person? He has to forgive
in any case. But the strength of a Sahaja Yogi can forgive.

00:24:18.168 --> 00:24:22.008
So, if somebody says something
against the divinity itself,

00:24:22.048 --> 00:24:25.728
you have to stand up in a way, in a dignified way.

00:24:25.755 --> 00:24:31.948
And use your discretion and if necessary, you
have to tell them that “you are in for trouble”.

00:24:31.966 --> 00:24:33.986
This much I can say,

00:24:33.993 --> 00:24:40.086
because this is also an important part where, step
by step, as you are growing, you will be amazed

00:24:40.103 --> 00:24:48.002
that as you are flowers, you are also the
thorns that have to protect the flower within.

00:24:48.942 --> 00:24:54.542
We have both roles and we are not to avoid
anything that is within us, that is our path.

00:24:54.542 --> 00:24:57.482
But the only thing is the channelising,

00:24:57.535 --> 00:25:01.725
this is very important and this
subtle point we must understand.

00:25:01.756 --> 00:25:07.165
Mr. Chavan is a very, very competent man and
he knows how to handle situations and things.

00:25:07.230 --> 00:25:17.009
But to him also and to everyone, I am telling, if you find anybody,
any Sahaja Yogi who is deviating from the path of Sahaja Yoga,

00:25:17.009 --> 00:25:22.737
you have to tell him, straight
on the face that, “This is wrong.

00:25:22.737 --> 00:25:26.929
This you should not do”. And you
should support a man who says that,

00:25:26.964 --> 00:25:32.794
it’s important. Because all of us must join hands
together to find out the weaknesses that we have

00:25:32.808 --> 00:25:36.234
and how to get rid of them. It’s very important.

00:25:36.261 --> 00:25:42.211
Because unless and until we take a strong attitude
towards ourselves and towards our whole collectivity,

00:25:42.241 --> 00:25:48.864
you don’t know there is such a tremendous force
collected against divinity that we may give in.

00:25:48.904 --> 00:25:57.764
So, let us build up ourselves also with courage and with the full
idea of our powers of divinity that we have within ourselves.

00:25:58.685 --> 00:26:01.795
May God bless you, it’s a very good point that came up, I am very happy.

00:26:01.833 --> 00:26:07.405
Mr. Chavan is a very good leader, a nice man
and compromising and a very powerful person.

00:26:07.405 --> 00:26:11.505
He comes from a community
which is known for its valour

00:26:11.549 --> 00:26:17.689
and so he is so strong because, he has built up himself like that

00:26:17.694 --> 00:26:20.949
and such a person will have patience
and everything he can have,

00:26:20.978 --> 00:26:29.888
but to a point, to a point. Then you have
to come out and tell off people.

00:26:29.929 --> 00:26:32.429
Thank you!

00:26:53.306 --> 00:27:13.428
