00:35:14.077 --> 00:35:21.258
[Mr Modi asks a question in Marathi.]

00:36:59.918 --> 00:37:06.078
This is a primordial question. He is asking why it is
crossed here, see at the Agnya chakra, why it is crossed?

00:37:07.718 --> 00:37:11.028
What is the need to cross it at this point?

00:37:11.078 --> 00:37:15.963
You could have had it straight you see,
so there is no problem of crossing.

00:37:19.588 --> 00:37:25.601
So, I said that this I have done so I better answer
because nobody will be able to answer this question.

00:37:25.615 --> 00:37:28.668
[Marathi].     First I will tell in English.

00:37:28.698 --> 00:37:34.328
You see, the Agnya Chakra is placed
in charge of both the things,

00:37:34.370 --> 00:37:38.412
is one is for Mana means for superego and also for ego.

00:37:38.412 --> 00:37:42.982
Now, how do you control these two things?

00:37:42.982 --> 00:37:48.342
They are to be placed at one point, how do you get a
point out of two things? Unless and until you cross them,

00:37:48.378 --> 00:37:54.403
it is simple mathematics; you have to cross
them at a point where you fix up one centre.

00:37:56.981 --> 00:38:00.533
And this one centre should be
able to control both the things

00:38:00.533 --> 00:38:03.033
Now you might say, why not have two centres?

00:38:03.033 --> 00:38:06.393
Because see, they are so interdependent.

00:38:06.432 --> 00:38:14.233
If you raise ego your superego goes down. If
you raise your superego, the ego goes down.

00:38:14.233 --> 00:38:22.058
So, they are so interconnected that it has to be one point by
which you can control both of them and put them in the balance.

00:38:22.088 --> 00:38:26.518
Now, another problem is that if it is
crossed, you see we are not stopped by that.

00:38:26.562 --> 00:38:32.515
The basic problem is that how to control both
these things, and that’s why it is placed here

00:38:32.515 --> 00:38:41.272
but you must know that this crossing does not stop your movement of the Kundalini. Because Kundalini rises in the centre,

00:38:41.272 --> 00:38:52.690
not on the sides. When these two are crossing,
the centre in between here is inside the thing.

00:38:52.690 --> 00:39:01.690
Say, for example, there is a crossing between the two bores
and both the bores become, here, open like this, like this,

00:39:01.732 --> 00:39:03.713
so it can always open, no problem.

00:39:03.726 --> 00:39:08.593
But the communication is there, that's all, the
communications is there, but this opens out properly,

00:39:08.593 --> 00:39:11.813
but why this is closed is the point.

00:39:11.813 --> 00:39:19.253
It is closed because of the extremes of one, of another.
This is closed because this one is more or this one is more.

00:39:19.253 --> 00:39:27.753
Now, if you can somehow reduce the pressure and
bring them into a balanced way then this opens out.

00:39:27.800 --> 00:39:30.300
Now, how do you do it? It's very simple,

00:39:30.300 --> 00:39:33.803
that supposing your ego is more, what
do you do? Left side to right side,

00:39:33.832 --> 00:39:39.629
right you do seven times. And now see for yourself
raising your Kundalini if Agnya opens or not?

00:39:39.629 --> 00:39:44.372
Supposing your superego is more, you can feel
it. Then you raise your right to your left down.

00:39:44.391 --> 00:39:49.504
Right? Now you balance it and
so that the aperture opens out.

00:39:49.504 --> 00:39:57.851
When it is in balance, it opens out automatically. That’s
